OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith some long sunny spells through
OL,7,Fthe day. Some cloud bubbling up by
OL,8,Fafternoon, mainly towards the south.
OL,9,FWarm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with some sunny
OL,12,Fintervals. Some clear spells at first
OL,13,Ftonight but clouding over, perhaps a
OL,14,Flight shower.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FIt will be a cloudier day,
OL,17,Fperhaps with the odd shower, but it
OL,18,Fshould brighten up later in the day
OL,19,Fwith some warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
