OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,7,Fspells, though more cloud over Argyll
OL,8,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday. Perhaps some
OL,9,Fthundery showers later on Thursday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
